                        <h2>Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2<span>Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2</span></h2>
                        <h4>基于 Blob 存储构建的高度可缩放的安全 Data Lake Storage</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_storage_trial">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
